00:43:54.214 --> 00:43:57.051
But she begged me to help her
as she lay on the ground.

00:43:59.470 --> 00:44:00.471
No.

00:44:01.555 --> 00:44:02.556
You'll die.

00:44:05.059 --> 00:44:06.852
- Get down from there.
- No.

00:44:09.396 --> 00:44:11.315
I won't die easily, either.

00:44:12.941 --> 00:44:15.944
I'm pretty lucky

00:44:17.237 --> 00:44:19.156
and I'm a lot like my mom.

00:44:42.888 --> 00:44:45.474
I told you she shouldn't have a scar.

00:44:45.557 --> 00:44:47.643
How was I to know she'd jump?

00:44:47.726 --> 00:44:49.395
I told you so many times.

00:44:49.478 --> 00:44:52.523
She's no ordinary witch.
You can't upset her.

00:44:52.898 --> 00:44:55.401
We can't film a girl
with a bust-up head and broken leg.

00:44:56.068 --> 00:44:57.945
How are we to wait until she heals?

00:44:58.028 --> 00:45:00.239
Forget the money.
Send her away already!

00:45:00.322 --> 00:45:02.199
No way! She's worth a fortune.

00:45:03.742 --> 00:45:07.496
You don't have to listen
to the bad things grown-ups say.

00:45:10.165 --> 00:45:11.583
Why are you crying?

00:45:13.127 --> 00:45:15.754
I read your diary.

00:45:17.214 --> 00:45:18.215
DIARY
BAEK AH JIN

00:45:18.298 --> 00:45:20.092
I also know what X means.

00:45:22.678 --> 00:45:25.139
X gets angry
only when Jun Seo isn't around.

00:45:25.222 --> 00:45:27.224
I'm so sad when Jun Seo isn't around.

00:45:27.307 --> 00:45:28.767
X is such a bad grown-up.

00:45:28.851 --> 00:45:30.811
I hope Jun Seo takes my side.

00:45:30.894 --> 00:45:32.604
I don't want to go to an orphanage.

00:45:32.688 --> 00:45:34.565
I can't make X angry.

00:45:37.401 --> 00:45:40.863
Then you must know
X is a bad grown-up.

00:45:42.531 --> 00:45:43.532
I know.

00:45:44.032 --> 00:45:45.033
I'm sorry.

00:45:45.743 --> 00:45:48.245
You looked after me all night.

00:45:48.954 --> 00:45:50.497
Yet I didn't know about it.

00:45:50.581 --> 00:45:52.708
Do you still like X?

00:45:52.791 --> 00:45:55.294
No, I don't like her.

00:45:57.129 --> 00:45:58.505
I only like you, Ah Jin.

00:45:59.089 --> 00:46:01.508
You're the only nice person at home.

00:46:05.554 --> 00:46:06.555
"Home"?

00:46:07.639 --> 00:46:10.058
I might not be able to go back there.

00:46:11.226 --> 00:46:13.687
I might get kicked out.

00:46:14.229 --> 00:46:15.230
Says who?

00:46:15.939 --> 00:46:17.357
You won't get kicked out.

00:46:18.734 --> 00:46:21.320
I'll protect you so she can't do

00:46:22.446 --> 00:46:23.697
anything bad to you.

00:46:24.740 --> 00:46:26.033
Does that mean

00:46:26.366 --> 00:46:28.243
you'll always be on my side?

00:46:28.535 --> 00:46:31.163
Yes, I'm always on your side.

00:46:32.164 --> 00:46:35.292
So, Ah Jin,
don't ever let go of my hand.

00:46:36.043 --> 00:46:37.044
Okay?

00:46:59.107 --> 00:47:01.360
Ah Jin, are you all right?

00:47:01.985 --> 00:47:03.111
You're awake.

00:47:03.612 --> 00:47:04.613
Do you recognize me?

00:47:05.989 --> 00:47:07.407
How can't I

00:47:08.200 --> 00:47:10.285
when you're holding my hand so tight?

00:47:15.916 --> 00:47:17.918
Don't look at me like that.

00:47:18.001 --> 00:47:19.837
I'm not dead, am I?

00:47:19.920 --> 00:47:22.339
You were unconscious
for three days straight.

00:47:23.674 --> 00:47:24.675
What?

00:47:32.182 --> 00:47:33.267
What's the date today?

00:47:37.020 --> 00:47:39.982
The enrollment deadline
was two days ago.

00:47:42.192 --> 00:47:46.113
You didn't enroll in time,
so your admission was canceled.

00:47:46.196 --> 00:47:48.323
We texted you many times already.

00:47:49.867 --> 00:47:53.120
We already accepted
a student on the waiting list

00:47:53.203 --> 00:47:55.205
so I'm sorry about your situation.

00:47:55.289 --> 00:47:57.040
But there's nothing
we can do to help--

00:48:07.217 --> 00:48:10.429
Ah Jin, we graduate tomorrow.
Will you be at the ceremony?

00:48:11.471 --> 00:48:13.682
Yes, of course.

00:48:41.668 --> 00:48:42.669
Thank you.

00:49:09.112 --> 00:49:11.865
CONGRATULATIONS
ON YOUR GRADUATION

00:49:16.203 --> 00:49:18.372
Ah Jin, why are you still here?

00:49:20.165 --> 00:49:21.458
Are you all right?

00:49:21.541 --> 00:49:23.293
I was worried when I heard
you were hospitalized.

00:49:23.669 --> 00:49:24.670
What happened to your face?

00:49:25.545 --> 00:49:27.339
I'm fine. I just fell.

00:49:27.756 --> 00:49:29.466
You should've been more careful.

00:49:29.549 --> 00:49:31.385
Congratulations on graduating.

00:49:31.468 --> 00:49:32.469
I'll take a photo for you.

00:49:35.389 --> 00:49:36.682
Are you ready?

00:49:36.765 --> 00:49:38.308
One, two, three.

00:49:40.268 --> 00:49:41.269
Smile a bit, will you?

00:49:41.812 --> 00:49:43.480
One, two...

00:49:52.489 --> 00:49:53.532
Jun Seo.

00:49:54.616 --> 00:49:55.951
I'm sorry I got here so late.

00:49:57.202 --> 00:49:59.121
Congratulations on graduating.

00:49:59.413 --> 00:50:00.706
Let's take some photos. Let's go.

00:50:04.668 --> 00:50:07.838
Did you hear from your grandpa?

00:50:07.921 --> 00:50:09.506
Does he know you're graduating?

00:50:09.881 --> 00:50:10.882
Yes.

00:50:10.966 --> 00:50:13.135
How? Did you tell him?

00:50:14.219 --> 00:50:15.303
Yes.

00:50:15.679 --> 00:50:17.264
Did he say anything?

00:50:18.181 --> 00:50:21.351
About a graduation present
or something.

00:50:21.935 --> 00:50:22.936
Like what?

00:50:23.395 --> 00:50:26.815
I mean you're an adult now

00:50:26.898 --> 00:50:29.526
so he might have prepared
something special--

00:50:29.609 --> 00:50:31.153
Take this, Mom.

00:50:31.236 --> 00:50:33.113
I'll eat with my friends.

00:50:33.196 --> 00:50:34.740
Wait, Jun Seo. My gosh.

00:50:43.123 --> 00:50:44.875
- Get in here.
- One, two, three.

00:50:45.333 --> 00:50:46.334
Look here, Mom.

00:51:25.874 --> 00:51:28.293
Thief! Catch that thief!

00:51:29.294 --> 00:51:30.587
Oh, no!

00:51:34.091 --> 00:51:35.801
He's a pickpocket!

00:51:44.768 --> 00:51:45.769
You asshole!

00:52:16.550 --> 00:52:19.845
If I hadn't cross paths
with that man then

00:52:21.346 --> 00:52:24.057
his life would've been
completely different.

00:52:26.685 --> 00:52:27.727
It's such a shame.

00:52:33.024 --> 00:52:35.610
The newbie's just 20 years old?

00:52:35.694 --> 00:52:37.737
He was sent here
from a youth detention center.

00:52:37.821 --> 00:52:40.532
His skin is so smooth and firm.

00:52:40.949 --> 00:52:42.033
I did, too, once.

00:52:43.034 --> 00:52:44.035
Jeez.

00:52:45.120 --> 00:52:46.121
What's he in for?

00:52:47.205 --> 00:52:48.999
Murder, but not just any kind.

00:52:49.708 --> 00:52:51.293
Patricide. My gosh.

00:52:51.751 --> 00:52:54.629
That young guy killed his dad?

00:52:54.713 --> 00:52:56.548
Kids these days are fearless.

00:52:56.631 --> 00:52:59.176
I talked to him a bit,
and he's pretty docile.

00:52:59.634 --> 00:53:03.346
He got bullied so much
at the youth detention center.

00:53:03.889 --> 00:53:05.182
He could've stayed there

00:53:05.599 --> 00:53:07.267
but he chose to be transferred here.

00:53:14.482 --> 00:53:19.070
DEAR X

00:55:39.169 --> 00:55:41.171
